Localization.Name: Veil Flash Hider3
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: ArmaMod
Type: Flash Hider
Attachment Point: Barrel
Size: 3

Recoil Stability: +15%
Recoil Smoothness: +15%

The Veil Flash Hider3 is an S3 flash hider from ArmaMod. Designed to reduce muzzle flash, it will help keep your position hidden once the action begins.
